      • scrapeWebpage

        public java.lang.String scrapeWebpage​(java.lang.String websiteLink)
        Parameters:
        websiteLink - used in Main method. Upon creation of WebpageHandling object the private String webAddress is called here
        headings - gathers all HTML lines that are encapsulated in h3 tags
        allHeadingsText - converts headings to a string without h3 tag encapsulation
        allLowerCaseHeadingsText - converts allHeadingsText words to all lower case letters.
        delimitedHeadingsText - separates string value allLowerCaseHeadingsText using regex "[\\n|\\s+|.|,|:] stores as Array"
        convertedHeadingArrayList - converts delimitedHeadingsText to ArrayList to merge for word count.
        boldedNames - gathers all HTML lines that are encapsulated in b tags
        allBoldedText - converts boldedNames to a string without b tag encapsulation
        allLowerCaseBoldText - converts allBoldedText words to all lower case letters.
        delimtedBoldedText - separates string value allLowerCaseBoldText using regex "[\\n|\\s+|.|,|:] to store as an Array"
        convertedBoldArrayList - converts delimtedBoldedText to ArrayList to merge for word count.
        spokenLines - gathers all HTML lines that are encapsulated in a[name] tags
        allSpokenText - converts spokenLines to a string without b tag encapsulation
        allLowerCaseSpokenText - converts allSpokenText words to all lower case letters.
        delimitedSpokenText - separates string value allLowerCaseSpokenText using regex "[\\n|\\s+|.|,|:] to store as an Array"
        convertedSpokenArrayList - converts delimitedSpokenText to ArrayList to merge for word count.
        mergedList - Combines all previous ArrayLists for word count
        Returns:
        Sorted string output formated in viewResults TextArea for GUI use in Main Application
